HEADWORD: Saccharate
<hw>Sac"cha*rate</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld>
<sd>(a)</sd> <def>A salt of saccharic acid.</def> <sd>(b)</sd> <def>In a
